## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Start the server with `npm start` and verify it launches without errors
- Test all API endpoints via the browser/frontend
- Verify WebSocket connections deliver real-time updates

### Manual Verification
- Navigate through every page of the SPA
- Confirm heatmap renders with live-updating density data
- Place a food order and watch status progress in real-time
- Trigger an emergency alert and verify it appears in the dashboard
- Test responsive layout at mobile and desktop breakpoints

## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Authentication**: I'll use simple JWT auth with a demo login (pre-seeded user). No OAuth/social login. Is that acceptable?

> [!NOTE]
> **Data simulation**: Since there's no real stadium hardware, the `simulator.js` service will generate realistic fluctuating crowd/queue data on timers. The app will feel "alive" with constantly updating numbers.
